title: Doctor Who - The Commentaries - S04E02 - The Fires of Pompeii
description:
Doctor Who - The Commentaries - S04E02 - The Fires of Pompeii

This is the 29 minute version...   

Last week, BBC PODcast (and had up for download) a full 48 minute version of S04E01, yet this week the version that was podcast and for download is only 29 minutes.   I THINK the ful 48 minute version will be on BBC7 (can someone please record that and share it?) and starting with Episode 03 there are only supposed to be one version (the full 48 minutes) from then on.
